name: wgdfstrategy
description: Collection of strategies to convert complex data structures from one GDF ( generic data format ) to another GDF. You may use the module to serialize complex data structure to string or deserialize string back to the original data structure. Generic data format ( GDF ) is a format of data structure designed with taking into account none unique feature of data so that it is applicable to any kind of data.
